name: クモ 〇〇二、HIMEIJI 2017
description:
The cloud above the Himeiji Castle in Kobe, Japan.
Shaving like cotton candies floating in the sky. 

The Cloud photo creation is inspiring from my trip that I have been to many place all round asia. The moment when your eye captured the big sky above any object on earth made me feel belong to this world. The greatness of nature made I feel more humble and realized that our life is just a part of the universe.
